propDescriptions.classes: 覆盖或扩展应用于组件的样式。请参阅下面 CSS API 了解更多详情。
propDescriptions.component: 用于根节点的组件。可以是一个字符串来使用 HTML 元素，也可以是一个组件。
propDescriptions.expandText:
覆盖扩展按钮的默认标签。
为了本地化，您可以使用提供的 翻译
propDescriptions.itemsAfterCollapse: If max items is exceeded, the number of items to show after the ellipsis.
propDescriptions.itemsBeforeCollapse: If max items is exceeded, the number of items to show before the ellipsis.
propDescriptions.maxItems: Specifies the maximum number of breadcrumbs to display. When there are more than the maximum number, only the first itemsBeforeCollapse and last itemsAfterCollapse will be shown, with an ellipsis in between.
propDescriptions.sx: The system prop that allows defining system overrides as well as additional CSS styles. See the `sx` page for more details.

root.description: Styles applied to the root element.
